                    <p>Perform routine database optimization including index rebuilding, statistics updates, and cleanup of temporary tables.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <h6>Affected Systems</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Web Portal</li>
